name: Gnaw
summary: With enough time and determination, you can chew through nearly anything.
description:
With enough time and determination, you can chew through nearly anything. You deal double your jaws damage to an unattended, inanimate object.Traits

Ratfolk: A creature with this trait is a member of the ratfolk ancestry. Ratfolk are humanoids who resemble rats. An ability with this trait can be used or selected only by ratfolk.
